GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/chinas-commerce-ministry-hold-anti-dumping-hearing-eu-brandy-imports-2024-07-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国拒绝西方在联合国会议上提出的人权改革的重要呼吁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rejects-key-western-calls-human-rights-reforms-un-meeting-2024-07-04/</link><description>中国周四拒绝了西方主导的人权改革建议，包括要求香港和新疆维吾尔人享有更大自由的呼吁，但接受了盟友的其他建议，试图在联合国会议上捍卫自己的记录。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 17:38:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rejects-key-western-calls-human-rights-reforms-un-meeting-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟公布了中国电动汽车关税计算</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-lays-out-its-china-ev-tariff-calculations-2024-07-04/</link><description>欧盟委员会周四公布了对中国电动汽车市场为期九个月的调查结果，深入了解了其计算关税的方式以及为支持其最引人注目的贸易案件而收集的证据。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 15:50:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-lays-out-its-china-ev-tariff-calculations-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国需求疲软削弱印度钻石出口，行业寻求支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/weak-chinese-demand-dents-indias-diamond-exports-industry-seeks-support-2024-07-04/</link><description>一家主要贸易机构负责人周四表示，由于主要市场中国的需求疲软，印度的切割和成品钻石出口一直步履蹒跚，除非政府向该行业提供支持，否则出口不太可能稳定下来。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 11:36:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/weak-chinese-demand-dents-indias-diamond-exports-industry-seeks-support-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>华为高管否认先进芯片短缺将阻碍中国人工智能雄心的观点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-exec-rejects-idea-that-advanced-chip-shortage-will-hamper-chinas-ai-2024-07-04/</link><description>中国科技巨头华为（HWT.UL）的一位高管周四驳斥了最先进人工智能芯片的短缺将阻碍中国成为人工智能领导者的目标的观点，但表示需要创新来解决这个问题。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 11:27:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/huawei-exec-rejects-idea-that-advanced-chip-shortage-will-hamper-chinas-ai-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟电动汽车关税决定后，名爵、蔚来暗示今年汽车价格上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mg-nio-hint-car-price-increases-this-year-following-eu-ev-tariff-decision-2024-07-04/</link><description>在欧盟决定确认对中国进口电动汽车征收关税后，中国品牌名爵和蔚来周四表示，他们可能会在今年晚些时候提高在欧洲的汽车价格。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 11:23:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mg-nio-hint-car-price-increases-this-year-following-eu-ev-tariff-decision-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>对欧盟对中国制造的电动汽车征收关税的反应</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/reaction-eu-duties-china-built-evs-2024-07-04/</link><description>欧盟将从周五起对中国制造的电动汽车进口征收高达37.6%的临时关税，这将加剧欧盟迄今为止最大贸易案中与北京的紧张关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 10:18:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/reaction-eu-duties-china-built-evs-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>独家：在死刑威胁后，企业考虑将台湾员工撤出中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/firms-weigh-removing-taiwan-staff-china-after-death-penalty-threat-2024-07-04/</link><description>四位知情人士表示，在北京表示可能对“顽固”台独分裂分子判处死刑后，一些外国公司正在考虑将台湾员工迁出中国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 09:40:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/firms-weigh-removing-taiwan-staff-china-after-death-penalty-threat-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国制造的电动汽车在迄今为止最大的欧盟贸易案件中被征收关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-imposes-duties-china-built-evs-leaving-four-months-talks-2024-07-04/</link><description>欧盟官员表示，欧盟将从周五起对中国制造的电动汽车进口征收高达37.6%的关税，这加剧了布鲁塞尔迄今为止最大贸易案中与北京的紧张关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 09:30:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-imposes-duties-china-built-evs-leaving-four-months-talks-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>中国和欧盟就即将实施的电动汽车关税举行技术会谈</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-eu-held-technical-talks-impending-ev-tariffs-2024-07-04/</link><description>中国商务部在例行新闻发布会上表示，中国和欧洲就中国电动汽车关税问题举行了多轮技术谈判，欧盟委员会将于周四确认这一消息。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 08:41:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-eu-held-technical-talks-impending-ev-tariffs-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉汽车首次进入中国政府采购清单</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-cars-first-time-chinese-government-purchase-list-2024-07-04/</link><description>据中国官方媒体澎湃新闻周四报道，特斯拉最畅销的 Model Y 被列入中国地方政府可以购买作为服务车的电动和插电式混合动力车型清单。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 08:17:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-cars-first-time-chinese-government-purchase-list-2024-07-04/</guid></item><item><title>习近平和普京阐述了欧亚安全俱乐部的雄心</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/xi-putin-set-out-ambitions-eurasian-security-club-2024-07-04/</link><description>中国国家主席习近平和俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京周四强调，广大欧亚地区国家之间应加强安全、政治和经济合作，以制衡西方联盟。</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jul 2024 07:34:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/xi-putin-set-out-ambitions-eurasian-security-club-2024-07-04/</guid></item></channel></rss>